&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;You will serve as the enterprise owner for SOX business process controls, partnering across Accounting, Finance, Operations, Product, Engineering, Compliance, Legal, Risk, and Internal Audit to protect the integrity of financial reporting.&lt;/p&gt;
